	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />When channel 3 is turned off using the bit in the NR30 register, it outputs 0v.
<br />If shift is set to 0% (&gt;&gt;4) it outputs -1v.
<br />(at least I THINK this is right... blargg?)
<br />
<br />LN

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


